Package: macroverse
Title: Macroverse - Complete Ecosystem for Large-Scale Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", 
           email = "benjaminpeeters@protonmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Meta-package that loads the complete macroverse ecosystem for
    international economic and social data analysis. Provides a unified interface
    to mvcommon (utilities), pplot (visualization), isomapper (country codes),
    macrodata (data access), and mvlazy (convenience functions).
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    mvcommon (>= 0.1.0),
    pplot (>= 0.1.0),
    isomapper (>= 0.1.0),
    macrodata (>= 0.1.0),
    mvlazy (>= 0.1.0)
Remotes:
    macroverse-r/mvcommon,
    macroverse-r/pplot,
    macroverse-r/isomapper,
    macroverse-r/macrodata,
    macroverse-r/mvlazy
